# Useful Display Filters

Contains string:

```
frame contains "password"
```

Contains text:

```
tcp contains "login"
```

Packet length:

```
frame.len > 500
```

TCP SYN packets:

```
tcp.flags.syn == 1 && tcp.flags.ack == 0
```

TCP Reset:

```
tcp.flags.reset == 1
```

HTTP Status Code:

```
http.response.code == 200
```

